  "texts": [
    "Part of this game is my revealing at this point what's behind one of the doors you didn't choose.",
    "let me show you what's behind Door 3.\"",
    "Door 3 opens to reveal a cute but very -economically speaking -unsavory donkey.",
    "Monty now to Jones: \"Do you want to switch to Door 2, or stay with Door 1?",
    "You'll get what's behind the door of your choice, and our game will end.\""
